00:00:59.259 --> 00:01:06.610
Key Point #1 - Push the ball at speed using
the inside of your dominant foot across your

00:01:06.610 --> 00:01:08.510
body towards your non dominant foot.

00:01:08.510 --> 00:01:10.949
The speed of this push is important.

00:01:10.949 --> 00:01:15.770
If the ball is moving to slow the defender
will have a better chance to win it.

00:01:15.770 --> 00:01:23.800
Remember it's a push, don't kick the ball.

00:01:23.800 --> 00:01:34.140
Key Point #2 - Make sure the ball doesn't
move forward toward the defender.

00:01:34.140 --> 00:01:36.949
You want it to move across your body.

00:01:36.949 --> 00:01:41.409
Keep your toe up when you push the ball and
this will help keep better control versus

00:01:41.409 --> 00:01:43.040
having your toe pointed down.

00:01:43.040 --> 00:01:48.839
Key Point #3 - Pass the ball forward to yourself
2-3 steps ahead of you and past the defender

00:01:48.839 --> 00:01:51.470
with the inside of your non dominant foot.

00:01:51.470 --> 00:01:57.189
This touch forward will be more like a pass
or kick versus a push like your first touch.

00:01:57.189 --> 00:02:02.490
If there are no other defenders around you
then your touch forward can be 3-5 steps.

00:02:02.490 --> 00:02:07.549
If there are other defenders nearby then take
a smaller touch of 1-2 steps

00:02:07.549 --> 00:02:13.160
The reason you take a bigger touch when no
defenders are around is so you can run faster

00:02:13.160 --> 00:02:14.160
towards the ball.

00:02:14.160 --> 00:02:19.309
Naturally you can run faster without the ball
at your feet, then with it.

00:02:19.309 --> 00:02:24.140
Plus now you can get your eyes up the field
versus staring down at the ball.

00:02:24.140 --> 00:02:27.590
Key Point #4 - Change pace!

00:02:27.590 --> 00:02:32.609
No matter what move you do the most important
thing to do afterwards is change pace.

00:02:32.609 --> 00:02:39.230
The La Croqueta is typically done at a medium
to slow running pace, but once the move has

00:02:39.230 --> 00:02:43.690
been executed be all Iniesta like and accelerate
to escape your defender.

00:02:43.690 --> 00:02:45.120
That's it for the key points.

