00:03:04.120 --> 00:03:06.380
You will need a ball and 4 cones for this
exercise.

00:03:06.380 --> 00:03:09.990
We will set up this exercise in 3 parts.

00:03:09.990 --> 00:03:16.389
Part 1 - Practice doing the La Croqueta without
the ball from a stand still to get your body

00:03:16.389 --> 00:03:19.660
use to how it will feel.

00:03:19.660 --> 00:03:22.389
Part 2 - Now practice with the ball from a
stand still.

00:03:22.389 --> 00:03:26.540
Go slow in the beginning and then as you feel
comfortable increase the speed of the move.

00:03:26.540 --> 00:03:29.380
Do the move, change pace then repeat.

00:03:29.380 --> 00:03:31.949
Part 3 - Set up four cones.

00:03:31.949 --> 00:03:38.370
A start cone and 5 yards ahead of it are two
cones about 2-3 steps apart from each other.

00:03:38.370 --> 00:03:42.059
Then place your end cone about 10 yards up
the field.

00:03:42.059 --> 00:03:47.190
Dribble by walking slowly up to the cone on
your dominant foot side, for me this would

00:03:47.190 --> 00:03:53.619
be the cone on my right side, do the La Croqueta,
don't let the ball hit the cones, then accelerate

00:03:53.619 --> 00:03:55.080
to the top cone as fast as you can.

00:03:55.080 --> 00:03:57.169
Light jog back and repeat.

00:03:57.169 --> 00:04:01.350
Once you are comfortable from a walk, then
start increasing your run up speed up to a

00:04:01.350 --> 00:04:03.210
medium pace.

00:04:03.210 --> 00:04:16.730
Repeat until you master it!

00:04:16.730 --> 00:04:22.050
If the defender is winning the ball all the
time then you may be to close to the defender.

00:04:22.050 --> 00:04:26.740
You want to be about a step away from them
when you do the move, not right on top of

00:04:26.740 --> 00:04:27.740
them.

00:04:27.740 --> 00:04:29.240
Keep your speed of the move up too.

00:04:29.240 --> 00:04:33.552
If the ball is pushed to slow across your
body that will give the defender plenty of

00:04:33.552 --> 00:04:37.570
time to get their foot out and win it.

00:04:37.570 --> 00:04:39.210
Make a play!

00:04:39.210 --> 00:04:43.840
Once you beat a defender with Iniesta's La
Croqueta then make a play.

00:04:43.840 --> 00:04:46.170
Don't try to dribble 3 more defenders.

00:04:46.170 --> 00:04:49.770
Get your shot, pass or cross off and make
a play.

00:04:49.770 --> 00:04:55.540
Yes, be confident and take players on but
get your teammates involved in the game; don't

00:04:55.540 --> 00:04:57.790
always try to do everything yourself.

00:04:57.790 --> 00:04:59.010
It's a team game.

